# 🚀 KanuorieTechLib

Fullstack learning platform.

## 🧩 Tech Stack
- Frontend: React + Vite
- Backend: Node.js + Express
- Database: PostgreSQL + Sequelize

## 📦 Setup

### Install all
npm install
cd backend && npm install
cd ../frontend && npm install

### Run full app
npm run dev

## 🌐 API Base URL
http://localhost:5000/api